    </objective>
    <objective>Compare and contrast various theories of privacy from social psychology and social science.
      <covers standard="acm-csec2017" knowledgeArea="6/5" id="1"/>
    </objective>
    <objective>Explain three properties commonly used for authentication.
      <covers standard="acm-csec2017" knowledgeArea="5" id="7"/>
